    • 字段详细资料

      • DEFAULT_WEIGHT_MATRIX

        public static final WeightMatrix DEFAULT_WEIGHT_MATRIX
        DEFAULT_WEIGHT_MATRIX provides a default weight matrix for an RNA Metric. Currently this is RNA.SimpleEditDistanceMatrix.

      • DEFAULT_METRIC

        public static final SequenceFragmentMetric DEFAULT_METRIC
        DEFAULT_METRIC provides a default metric for an RNA Table. Currently this is an WHDGlobalSequenceFragmentMetric defined over the DEFAULT_WEIGHT_MATRIX
